column16: Anthony Rendon singles on a ground ball to left fielder Kirk Nieuwenhuis.
Denard Span homers (5) on a fly ball to right center field.    Asdrubal Cabrera scores.
Scott Hairston called out on strikes.
Jose Lobaton flies out to left fielder Kirk Nieuwenhuis.
Asdrubal Cabrera doubles (29) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Kirk Nieuwenhuis.
Adam LaRoche flies out to center fielder Juan Lagares.
Corey Dickerson grounds out softly, catcher Travis d'Arnaud to first baseman Eric Campbell.   Justin Morneau to 2nd.
Christian Yelich singles on a line drive to right fielder Kirk Nieuwenhuis.   Adeiny Hechavarria scores.
